quran[40]{c,v,t}:
  19,59,"Lontii Й“aawo maЙ“Й“e lontotooЙ“e, Й“e yeebi Julde nden Й“e jokki welnuruuji Й—in aray Й“e hawroya e bone"
  19,60,"Si wanaa on tuubuЙ—o o gomЙ—ini o golli ko moЖҙЖҙi, Й“en Й—on Й“e naatay Aljanna on Й“e tooГұiroy- taake hay e huunde"
  19,61,"Aljannaaji Adan Й—in Й—i Hinnorante On Fodi jeyaaЙ“e Makko Й“en e birnagal, pellet Kanko, Fodoore Makko nden laatike ko aroore"
  19,62,"ЖҒe nanataa nder ton rayrayti si wonaa kisiyee, no woodani Й“e arsike maЙ“Й“e on nder ton bimmbi e kiikiiЙ—e"
  19,63,"On Aljanna mo Men Roninta immorde e jeyaaЙ“e Amen Й“en, on laatiiЙ—o kulo [Alla]"
  19,64,"Men jippotaako si wanaa e Yamaruyee Joomi maaЙ—a, no woodani Mo ko woni kon hedde yeeso amen e ko woni kon Й“aawo amen e ko woni kon hakkunde Й—um, Joomi maaЙ—a laataaki yejjitoowo"
  19,65,"Jooma kammuuli Й—in e leydi ndin e ko woni kon hakkunde majji, Rewu mo monГұitor Dewal Makko. Taw si hiЙ—a anndani Mo tokoraajo"
  19,66,"NeЙ—Й—anke on no wi'a: \"Eyoo, e jaka si mi maai aroyay ka mi yaltinee tawa ko mi wuuruЙ—o"
  19,67,"Enee, neЙ—Й—anke on annditaali Menen Men Tagiino mo ko adii, hari o wonaali hay e huunde"
  19,68,"Mi woondirii Joomi maaЙ—a Men mooЙ“ay Й“e sanne e Seytanuuji Й—in, refti Men adda Й“e sara Jahannama ko Й“e jiccii Й“e"
  19,69,Refti Men Й—oofa immorde e kala fedde ko hommbo e maЙ“Й“e Й“urnoo saЙ—tude dartagol e dow Hinnorante On
  19,70,Refti ko Menen Anndi Й“en Й“urЙ“e hanndude e sumugol e magge
  19,71,"Alaa hay e gooto e mo'on si wanaa o joloyay e magge, Й—um laatike e dow Joomi maaЙ—a ko Г‘aawaaЙ—um Tentinaa"
  19,72,"Refti Men ndannda Й“en hulunooЙ“e [Alla] Men Й—ala tooГұooЙ“e Й“en ko Й“e jicciiЙ“e nder ton"
  19,73,"Si janngaama e taweede maЙ“Й“e Aayeeje Amen ЖҒannguЙ—e Й—en; yedduЙ“e Й“en wi'ana gom- Й—imЙ“e Й“en: \"Ko honnde e feddeeji Й—in Й—iЙ—i Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude darnde Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude kadi mbatu"
  19,74,Heewii ko Men halki ado maЙ“Й“e immorde e gire tawi ko kamЙ“e Й“uri fotude mirannji suudu e mbaadi
  19,75,"Maaku: \"On laatiiЙ—o e nder majjere nden yo Hinnorante fontan mo fontudee, haa si Й“e yi'ii ko Й“e fodaa kon, si tawii ko lepte Й—en maa si ko Darngal ngal, aray Й“e annda on m bonuЙ—o nukkuure e Й“urЙ—o lo'ude konu"
  19,76,"Alla no Й“eydana Й“en feewuЙ“e Peewal, MoЖҙЖҙi heddotooЙ—i Й—in Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude mbarjaari ka Joomi maaЙ—a Й“uri moЖҙЖҙude kadi ruttorde"
  19,77,"Enee, a yi'ii on yedduЙ—o Aayeeje Amen Й—en, o wi'i: \"Maatun mi okkee jawdi e Й“iЙ—Й—o"
  19,78,"Enee o Жҙelliti e ko wirnii kon, kaa jogiti ka Hinnorante Aadi"
  19,79,"Wanaa non, aray Men winnda ko o wi'ata kon Men Й“eydana mo immorde e Lepte Й—en Й“eydude"
  19,80,"Men Rona mo e ko o wi'ata kon, o ara e Amen ko o weddiiЙ—o(gooto)"
  19,81,ЖҒe jogitii gaanin Alla reweteeЙ—i fii yo Й—i laatano Й“e teddungal. @Corrected
  19,82,"Wonaa non, maЙ“e yedda rewugolЙ“e ngol, Й“e laatanoo Й“e ayЙ“e"
  19,83,Enee a yi'aali Menen Men Nulii Seytanuuji e dow yedduЙ“e Й“en hiЙ—i Жҙuuna Й“e Жҙuunudee
  19,84,"Wata a hawjan Й“e, pellat, limonayЙ“ebe limugol"
  19,85,"Г‘alnde Men mooЙ“oyta hulooЙ“e [Alla] Й“en ka Hinnorante TeddinaaЙ“e"
  19,86,Men sogga bomЙ“e Й“en haa ka Jahannama ko Й“e jolooЙ“e
  19,87,ЖҒe maraa tefoore nden si wanaa on jogitiiЙ—o ka Hinnorante Aadi
  19,88,"ЖҒe wi'i: \"Hinnorante jogitike Й“iЙ—Й—o"
  19,89,GomЙ—ii on addii huunde pankarЙ—ii nde. @Corrected
  19,90,Kammuuli Й—in no do'a(Й—esa) seekaade immorde e Й—um leydi ndin feera pelle Й—en uuya fii unagol
  19,91,fii Й“e noddanii Hinnorante Й“iЙ—Й—o
  19,92,Haananaa Hinnorante nde O jogitotoo Й“iЙ—Й—o. @Corrected
  19,93,Alaa wonЙ—o ka kammuuli e ka leydi si wanaa o aray ka Hinnorante hombo woni jeyaaЙ—o
  19,94,GomЙ—ii O moftii Й“e O limii Й“e kadi e limugol. @Corrected
  19,95,"[Gooto] Kala e maЙ“Й“e aray Mo Г‘alnde Darngal ko o woddiiЙ—o(teeldЙ—o)"
  19,96,"Pellet, Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e golli ko moЖҙЖҙi kon aray ka Hinnorante waЙ—anaЙ“e Giggol"
  19,97,"Anndu ko Men newiniri nde ka Й—enngal maaЙ—a; ko fii yo a weltinir nde hulooЙ“e [Alla] Й“en jertiniraa nde yimЙ“e saЙ—tuЙ“e wennje"
  19,98,"Heewii ko Men halki ado maЙ“Й“e e gire taw si hiЙ—a so'a e maЙ“Й“e immorde e goЙ—Й—o, maa hiЙ—a nana Й“e hito"